<bibRefCitation id="C54D4B6E075DFFC613B205DBFE5DA8CE" author="CRONIER C. &amp; COURVILLE P." box="[140,453,2001,2027]" pageId="37" pageNumber="60" pagination="999 - 1014" refId="ref30969" refString="CRONIER C. &amp; COURVILLE P. 2004. - A rich and highly endemic decapod crustacean fauna from the Middle Jurassic of north-east France. Palaeontology 47 (4): 999 - 1014. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 0031 - 0239.2004.00393. x" type="journal article" year="2004">Crônier &amp; Courville, 2004</bibRefCitation>
