<emphasis id="93A8EA8D075DFFC6173B03BDFB5EAEF5" box="[1029,1222,438,465]" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="60">S. pseudoventrosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Finally, there is an orbital row, which is absent in 
<taxonomicName id="66DC4D1C075DFFC617BA03DDFB60AED5" baseAuthorityName="Secretan" baseAuthorityYear="1964" box="[1156,1272,470,497]" class="Malacostraca" family="Erymidae" genus="Stenodactylina" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="37" pageNumber="60" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="australis">
<emphasis id="93A8EA8D075DFFC617BA03DDFB60AED5" box="[1156,1272,470,497]" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="60">S. australis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="66DC4D1C075DFFC6163803DDFA30AED5" baseAuthorityName="Cronier &amp; Courville" baseAuthorityYear="2004" box="[1286,1448,470,497]" class="Malacostraca" family="Erymidae" genus="Stenodactylina" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="37" pageNumber="60" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="burgundiaca">
<emphasis id="93A8EA8D075DFFC6163803DDFA30AED5" box="[1286,1448,470,497]" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="60">S. burgundiaca</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="66DC4D1C075DFFC6101303FDFC5FAD35" baseAuthorityName="Moret" baseAuthorityYear="1946" box="[813,967,502,529]" class="Malacostraca" family="Erymidae" genus="Stenodactylina" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="37" pageNumber="60" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="delphinensis">
<emphasis id="93A8EA8D075DFFC6101303FDFC5FAD35" box="[813,967,502,529]" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="60">S. delphinensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="66DC4D1C075DFFC610EB03FDFB09AD35" baseAuthorityName="Van Straelen" baseAuthorityYear="1925" box="[981,1169,502,529]" class="Malacostraca" family="Erymidae" genus="Stenodactylina" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="37" pageNumber="60" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="deslongchampsi">
<emphasis id="93A8EA8D075DFFC610EB03FDFB09AD35" box="[981,1169,502,529]" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="60">S. deslongchampsi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="66DC4D1C075DFFC617A103FDFB6EAD35" baseAuthorityName="Wright" baseAuthorityYear="1881" box="[1183,1270,503,529]" class="Malacostraca" family="Erymidae" genus="Stenodactylina" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="37" pageNumber="60" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="guisei">
<emphasis id="93A8EA8D075DFFC617A103FDFB6EAD35" box="[1183,1270,503,529]" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="60">S. guisei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName id="66DC4D1C075DFFC6160A03FDFA30AD35" baseAuthorityName="Stenzel" baseAuthorityYear="1945" box="[1332,1448,502,529]" class="Malacostraca" family="Erymidae" genus="Stenodactylina" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="37" pageNumber="60" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="triglypta">
<emphasis id="93A8EA8D075DFFC6160A03FDFA30AD35" box="[1332,1448,502,529]" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="60">S. triglypta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Considering all these elements, we consider this specimen as a representative of a new species of erymid lobsters: 
<taxonomicName id="66DC4D1C075DFFC61650003CFBA2AD55" authority="Devillez &amp; Charbonnier, 2021" authorityName="Devillez &amp; Charbonnier" authorityYear="2021" class="Malacostraca" family="Erymidae" genus="Stenodactylina" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="37" pageNumber="60" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="shotoverigiganti" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis id="93A8EA8D075DFFC61650003CFBA2AD55" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="60">Stenodactylina shotoverigiganti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="889B57F6075DFFC6177C005CFBE6AD55" box="[1090,1150,598,624]" pageId="37" pageNumber="60" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</paragraph>
